{
  "info": {
    "name": "Log.AI-CAMS — Playlists",
    "_postman_id": "d5e6f7a8-b9c0-1234-efff-456789012345",
    "description": "Playlist Management API — CMS (React & Flutter)\n\nBase URL: {{baseUrl}}\nAuth: Bearer {{accessToken}} (user) hoặc {{deviceAccessToken}} (PlaybackDevice)\n\nEndpoints:\n  GET    /api/playlists                             SA, BM, SM, PlaybackDevice ✅ (device: scope Store session)\n  GET    /api/playlists/{id}                        SA, BM, SM, PlaybackDevice ✅ (device: playlist.StoreId = session)\n  POST   /api/playlists                             BM, SM only\n  PUT    /api/playlists/{id}                        BM, SM only\n  DELETE /api/playlists/{id}                        BM, SM only\n  PUT    /api/playlists/{id}/toggle-status           BM, SM only\n  POST   /api/playlists/{id}/tracks                 BM, SM only\n  DELETE /api/playlists/{id}/tracks/{trackId}       BM, SM only\n  POST   /api/playlists/{id}/retranscode            BM, SM only\n\nKey rules:\n- Playlist has no BrandId; brand derived from playlist.Store.BrandId\n- BrandManager must provide storeId (must belong to their brand)\n- StoreManager: storeId auto-resolved from user.StoreId\n- trackIds in UpdatePlaylist: null=no-op, []=remove all, [ids]=sync\n- Auto-transcode triggered (debounced 5 min) on track add/remove\n- Retranscode: force re-generate HLS, bumps TranscodeVersion, clears HlsUrl\n\nEntityStatusEnum: Inactive=0, Active=1, Pending=2, Rejected=3\n\nSee: docs/playlists/API_Playlists.md",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "https://localhost:7001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "playlistId",
      "value": "p1000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "trackId",
      "value": "a1b2c3d4-0001-0000-0000-000000000001",
