              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/playlists",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "playlists"]
            },
            "description": "Create a new playlist.\n\nAuth: BrandManager ✅, StoreManager ✅\n\nNotes:\n- StoreManager: storeId is auto-resolved from user.StoreId (ignore storeId in body).\n- BrandManager: storeId is REQUIRED and must belong to their brand.\n- moodId must exist if provided.\n- name must be unique within the store.\n- trackIds is optional. Invalid track IDs (wrong brand) are silently ignored.\n- All inserts (Playlist + PlaylistTrack) in a single transaction."
          },
          "response": [
