        {
          "name": "Update Playlist",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Afternoon Chill (Extended)\",\n  \"description\": \"Extended version with more tracks\",\n  \"moodId\": null,\n  \"isDefault\": null,\n  \"trackIds\": null\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/playlists/{{playlistId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "playlists", "{{playlistId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Update an existing playlist (partial update / patch semantics).\n\nAuth: BrandManager (own brand) ✅, StoreManager (own store) ✅\n\nNotes:\n- trackIds semantics:\n  • null → do NOT touch track list\n  • [] → REMOVE ALL tracks from playlist\n  • [id1, id2] → SYNC: delete tracks not in list, add new ones (validates brand)\n- name uniqueness only re-checked if name actually changed.\n- moodId must exist if changed.\n- Scalar update + track sync in a single transaction.\n- After track changes: reindex OrderIndex in background."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK — Updated",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "PUT",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Afternoon Chill (Extended)\"\n}",
                  "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/playlists/{{playlistId}}",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "playlists", "{{playlistId}}"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
