        {
          "name": "Add Tracks to Playlist",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"trackIds\": [\n    \"a1b2c3d4-0003-0000-0000-000000000003\",\n    \"a1b2c3d4-0004-0000-0000-000000000004\"\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/playlists/{{playlistId}}/tracks",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "playlists", "{{playlistId}}", "tracks"]
            },
            "description": "Add one or more tracks to a playlist.\n\nAuth: BrandManager (own brand) ✅, StoreManager (own store) ✅\n\nNotes:\n- Duplicate track IDs in request are silently deduplicated.\n- Tracks already in playlist are skipped (not duplicated).\n- Track IDs not belonging to the brand are silently ignored.\n- After DB commit: OrderIndex reindexed in background; auto-transcode triggered (debounced 5 min)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK — Tracks added",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}", "type": "text" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
                ],
                "body": {
